  <brief_title>Green Tea Mouthwash on Generalized Plaque- Induced Gingivitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Green Tea Mouthwash on Generalized Plaque- Induced Gingivitis: A Randomized Controlled Clinical Trial</official_title>
