  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This investigation will study the effect of green tea mouthwash as an adjunctive therapy to
      mechanical treatment on gingival health, and whether it has any side effects. This study also
      aims at increasing the awareness among health professionals and the community regarding the
      benefits of natural herbal products such as green tea on oral health, opposed to common
      chemical products. This may provide an efficient alternative for people who are sensitive to
      certain chemical products or who have limited sources of income and cannot afford expensive
      treatment of dental problems.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
